    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I faced the same problem, &quot;Class file has wrong version 52.0, should be 50.0&quot; when running Java through <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Apache_Ant\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Ant</a>...</p>\n<p>All I did was adding <strong>fork=&quot;true&quot;</strong> wherever I used the <strong>javac</strong> task, and it worked...</p>\n"
