    "creation_date" : 1442217341,
    "answer_id" : 32559772,
    "question_id" : 28180915,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I have got the same error as in the header because of a failed attempt to compile my project with <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Java_version_history#Java_SE_8\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Java 8</a> and then reattempting to compile with <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Java_version_history#Java_SE_6\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Java 6</a>.</p>\n<p>Some classes where compiled at the first attempt with Java 8 and did not recompile with Java 6. Mixed classes did not compile then. Cleaning the project solved the problem.</p>\n<p>This answer is not strictly relevant to the question, but it could be useful for someone.</p>\n"
  }, {
