    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In your IntelliJ IDEA, find file <em>tools.jar</em>. Replace it with <em>tools.jar</em> from your <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Java_version_history#Java_SE_8\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">JDK 8</a>.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 9831764,
      "reputation" : 400,
      "user_id" : 7283201,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/eAHFK.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Sadman Sakib",
