    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 2,
    "last_activity_date" : 1605147749,
    "creation_date" : 1605147749,
    "answer_id" : 64796992,
    "question_id" : 28180915,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you are using <code>javac</code> to compile, and you get this error, then\nremove all the <code>.class</code> files</p>\n<pre><code>rm *.class     # On Unix-based systems\n</code></pre>\n<p>and recompile.</p>\n<pre><code>javac fileName.java\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
