      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "I had a similar problem &quot;class file has wrong version 61.0, should be 52.0&quot; for using the fundamental org.springframework.context.annotation.ComponentScan class! For me changing the JDK/JRE version didn&#39;t solve the problem. Then I downgraded spring-webmvc dependency version from 6.0.2 to 5.2.6.RELEASE and it eventually worked."
    } ],
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1360311,
