    "question_id" : 28180915,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If the error comes from an <strong>external dependency</strong> (<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Apache_Maven\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Maven</a>/<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gradle\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Gradle</a>), the version you imported requires a newer JDK. (<em>e.g., you imported <a href=\"https://github.com/ben-manes/caffeine\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Caffeine</a> 3.0.x which requires <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Java_version_history#Java_11\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Java 11</a>, but you are using <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Java_version_history#Java_SE_8\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Java 8</a>.</em>)</p>\n<p>Solution: downgrade the dependency to the latest version compatible with your JDK.</p>\n<p>Java version numbers can be found in <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Java_class_file#General_layout\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Java class file wiki page</a> (byte offset 6-7).</p>\n"
  }, {
